#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.58"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.58:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.58:0.2"
msgid "6. Puññābhisandavagga "
msgstr "6. Overflowing Merit "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: sudattaanāthapiṇḍikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.58:0.3"
msgid "58. Sudattasutta "
msgstr "58. Sudatta "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.58:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.64, sc2
msgctxt "an4.58:2.1"
msgid "“Bhojanaṃ, gahapati, dadamāno ariyasāvako paṭiggāhakānaṃ cattāri ṭhānāni deti. "
msgstr "“Householder, when a noble disciple gives food, they give the recipients four things. "

msgctxt "an4.58:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.58:2.3"
msgid "Āyuṃ deti, vaṇṇaṃ deti, sukhaṃ deti, balaṃ deti. "
msgstr "Long life, beauty, happiness, and strength. "

msgctxt "an4.58:2.4"
msgid "Āyuṃ kho pana datvā āyussa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. "
msgstr "Giving long life, they have long life as a god or human. … "

msgctxt "an4.58:2.5"
msgid "Vaṇṇaṃ datvā … sukhaṃ datvā … balaṃ datvā balassa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. "
msgstr "Giving beauty … happiness … strength … "

msgctxt "an4.58:2.6"
msgid "Bhojanaṃ, gahapati, dadamāno ariyasāvako paṭiggāhakānaṃ imāni cattāri ṭhānāni detīti. "
msgstr "When a noble disciple gives food, they give the recipients these four things. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.58:3.1"
msgid "Yo saññatānaṃ paradattabhojinaṃ, "
msgstr "Carefully giving food at the right time, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:3.2"
msgid "Kālena sakkacca dadāti bhojanaṃ; "
msgstr "to those who are disciplined, eating only what others give, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:3.3"
msgid "Cattāri ṭhānāni anuppavecchati, "
msgstr "you provide them with four things: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:3.4"
msgid "Āyuñca vaṇṇañca sukhaṃ balañca. "
msgstr "long life, beauty, happiness, and strength. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
#. VAR: vaṇṇadāyī → so āyudāyī baladāyī (bj, pts1) | āyudāyī baladāyī (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.58:4.1"
msgid "So āyudāyī vaṇṇadāyī, "
msgstr "A person who gives long life, beauty, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: sukhaṃ balaṃ dado → sukhaṃ vaṇṇaṃ dado (bj, s1-3, km) | sukhavaṇṇadado (pts1) | sukhabaladado (mr)
msgctxt "an4.58:4.2"
msgid "sukhaṃ balaṃ dado naro; "
msgstr "happiness, and strength, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:4.3"
msgid "Dīghāyu yasavā hoti, "
msgstr "has long life and fame "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:4.4"
msgid "yattha yatthūpapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "wherever they’re reborn.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.58:4.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
